              "messages": {
                "default": [
                  {
                    "cta": "Cool!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to give technical updates at work.\nYou will learn to talk about blockers, dependencies, and issues in your tasks.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/2beb47f0-b1e0-44ff-be57-bd7e4d447dda-Technical-update---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "When you are stuck on something, say:\n\"I'm stuck on [task] because [reason].\"\nFor example: \"I'm stuck on the API work because the docs aren't ready yet.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/2beb47f0-b1e0-44ff-be57-bd7e4d447dda-Technical-update---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "When your work depends on someone else's task, say:\n\"This depends on [task], which should be done by [day].\"\nFor example: \"This depends on the database update, which should be done by Thursday.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/2beb47f0-b1e0-44ff-be57-bd7e4d447dda-Technical-update---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "When you find a problem, say:\n\"We found [issue] in [task], so we [action taken].\"\nFor example: \"We found a bug in the build setup, so we rolled back for now.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/2beb47f0-b1e0-44ff-be57-bd7e4d447dda-Technical-update---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Now let's practice giving technical updates!",
                    "media": {
